{"search_data": "Uttar PradeshSamajwadi Pension Yojana to Cover 10 Lakh MoreBelow are the main facilities being provided under the Samajwadi Pension YojanaThe head of the family will be given Rs. 500 under the scheme for the first year.An increment of Rs. 50 will be done every year in the pension until it reaches Rs. 750.The pension amount will be paid via e-payment or direct transfer to the bank account.If the family has children between age of 6 to 14 years, they have to be admitted in the school, else the pension will be discontinued for the beneficiary.Complete details about the Samajwadi Pension Yojana in Hindi can be found at the link below http://sspy-up.gov.in/pdf/go.pdf (currently not working)The candidates can just check the official website http://sspy-up.gov.in/District Wise List of Samajwadi Pension Yojana Beneficiarieshttp://sspy-up.gov.in/SamajwadiPension_1516/OAPReportDistrictVise_15_16.aspxDownload Samajwadi Pension Yojana Application Formhttp://sspy-up.gov.in/pdf/avpatra.pdfThe applicants can also check the status of their application at the link below http://sspy-up.gov.in/SamajwadiPension/Search_Pensioner.aspx  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now  at  "}